e front and six in a comfortable passenger area), four Large creatures (one in the front and three in the back), or sixteen Small creatures (four in the front and twelve in the back). The limousine has the exterior color and design details you choose when
 you prepare the spell, and the interior is one of opulent luxury. You decide what its license plates look like when you cast the spell.
\par The }{\i\fs20\cf0 phantom limousine }{\fs20\cf0 has a Defense of 6, hardness of 15, and 50 hit points +1 point per caster level. If it loses all its hit points, the }{\i\fs20\cf0 phantom limousine }{\fs20\cf0 disappears. A }{\i\fs20\cf0 phantom limousine 
}{\fs20\cf0 is much faster than it looks, with a top speed of 60 feet per caster level, an initiative modifier of \endash 2, and a maneuver modifier of \endash 2.
\par A }{\i\fs20\cf0 phantom limousine }{\fs20\cf0 has enough luxurious food and drink inside to provide a hearty meal for all passengers. It has all the powers of a }{\i\fs20\cf0 phantom chopper }{\fs20\cf0 
(ability to drive over bad terrain, water, or air). Additionally, it is airtight and can even travel underwater at a speed of 10 feet per caster level.
