\i\fs20\cf0 Phantom bullets }{\fs20\cf0 count as having a +3 enhancement bonus for the purpose of overcoming damage reduction, although they don\rquote t actually receive the enhancement bonus on attacks or damage. Additionally, the }{\i\fs20\cf0 
phantom bullets }{\fs20\cf0 disappear 1d4 rounds after being fired, making it impossible to gather ballistic evidence.
